{
  "title": "Lively Norwegian Pork Skillet",
  "description": "A hearty, fatty pork skillet packed with sweet dark brown sugar, tangy pickles, and fresh cabbage for an energizing Norwegian feast.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
